CatDescriptText: Related article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 29, 1939, pg. 20, reads: "'Swings' 'Em - Little Genevieve, baton wielder for the Sunset Royals, hailed as one of the slickest em cees in business is creating a sensation with the band on its present tour."
